      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCESS ADA (8) scored two on end prior to a close up fourth (29.76) last time at this track, where she gave a sight after a scorching early split but weakened late to finish one length from the winner. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Rates on top in this line up. GRAMERCY GARRY (7) is a well performed dog and winner of 11 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at Dubbo (35.45). Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Cannot be left out. GYPSY GRACE (4) finished in the minors last start over the 520m at this track but ran a fast 29.83 last start. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. ASHBY GNOCCHI (5) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.",
